title: DDFP 343: Potential last to first teams
itunes:title: DDFP 343: Potential last to first teams
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to tackle your social media questions including which team won the 2014 NFL Draft, Marcus Mariota's best team fit and heads or tails? Plus, at 20:24, the guys debate which team in 2015 has the best chance at going from last to first in their division. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
